{"tid":649039,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一首歌，說盡每對情侶分手前都有過既階段","createTime":"2018-05-01T08:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T04:28:44.000Z","uid":43210,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f4936b13785241101c87187f4405cf84cc466b40","tid":649039,"uid":43210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"大學時代已很喜歡Maroon 5既歌，今日聽番nothing last forever，適逢和女友冷戰中，聽到想喊出黎<br />\n<br />\nIt is so easy to see<br />\nDysfunction between you and me<br />\nWe must free up these tired souls<br />\nBefore the sadness kills us both<br />\n<br />\n其實身邊好朋友，父母都睇得出我們之間存在問題，只係我唔想面對，已為時間會解決問題⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nIf you don't know, then you can't care<br />\nAnd you show up, but you're not there<br />\n<br />\n人在，心卻似不在<br />\n<br />\nEveryday, with worthless words, get us more far away<br />\n<br />\n每日都唔知講咩好，只係早晨、晚安，不再分享生活細節，好似漸行漸遠咁<br />\n<br />\nA bed that's warm with memories<br />\nCan heal us temporarily<br />\nBut misbehaving only makes<br />\nThe ditch between us so damn deep<br />\n<br />\n床上的激情或許暫時令我們忘記這些不快，但熱情過後呢，感覺好像更差<br />\n<br />\nThough we have not hit the ground<br />\nDoesn't mean we're not still falling<br />\nOh, I want so bad to pick you up<br />\nBut you're still too reluctant to accept my help<br />\n<br />\n雖然還未宣判死刑，但已感到離此不遠<br />\n想力挽狂瀾，但妳不想，我還有甚麼可以做<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=wC4l3LzLUUo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwC4l3LzLUUo&d=gCz%2Bn9pUQ%2BW1BqbAcjAdyaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=8a56ec09\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=wC4l3LzLUUo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔駛同我講帽事，我深信一對情侶關係本身係健康，第三者係唔會有位入，真係有解決唔到既問題，有同冇第三者，分手都係一個結果。"},{"pid":"c5e0dcd7711fdac0eb50ec5baf4a99b8b2519134","tid":649039,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"暨凎寘頞k&frac12;"},{"pid":"ee45a13f86fa9c8ae15797ec2bf404183b9c915e